lead_paragraph: Consider the release of this week's B.C.S. standings the calm before the storm. There was little activity of note, other than Stanford passing Boise State to move to No. 4 and Houston jumping up to 13.

headline.main: B.C.S. Standings Await Shake-Up After SEC Showdown
